<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='106227' id='t-106227'>on our life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='108938' id='t-108938'>Roberto D'Angelo: As you may imagine,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='110940' id='t-110940'>unfortunately, we were not ready.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='113236' id='t-113236'>Nobody taught us how to deal
with such kinds of disabilities,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='117291' id='t-117291'>and as many questions as possible started</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='119378' id='t-119378'>to come to our minds.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='121310' id='t-121310'>And that has been really a tough time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='124339' id='t-124339'>Questions, some basics, like, you know,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='126636' id='t-126636'>why did this happen to us?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='128816' id='t-128816'>And what went wrong?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='130811' id='t-130811'>Some more tough, like, really,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='133314' id='t-133314'>what will be the impact on Mario's life?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='135021' id='t-135021'>I mean, at the end,
will he be able to work?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='137141' id='t-137141'>Will he be able to be normal?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='138595' id='t-138595'>And, you know, as a parent,
