<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='141820' id='t-141820'>why is he not going to be better than us?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='145262' id='t-145262'>And this, indeed, really is tough to say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='148540' id='t-148540'>but a few months later, we realized that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='151328' id='t-151328'>we were really feeling like a failure.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='154588' id='t-154588'>I mean, the only real product of our life,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='157609' id='t-157609'>at the end, was a failure.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='159449' id='t-159449'>And you know, it was not a failure
