<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='175422' id='t-175422'>we started to look at him,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='177316' id='t-177316'>and we said, we have to react.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='179565' id='t-179565'>So immediately, as Francesca
